{"tid":1822571,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"小白轟巴塞不尊重華維迪：Ugly！","createTime":"2020-01-13T04:55:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T10:22:24.000Z","uid":31626,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"06b1f56878d63fba9f050304aa75a4a18ac14e8c","tid":1822571,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:55:52.000Z","msg":"【Now Sports-體育】巴塞隆拿斟介沙維回歸執教已是公開的秘密，前傳奇中場恩尼斯達批評這做法毫不尊重現任主帥華維迪。<br />\n<br />\n「巴塞隆拿的行為有點醜陋，你需要尊重現任教練，他們的做法傷害對方很深。」剛為神戶勝利船贏得日本天皇盃的恩尼斯達（Andres Iniesta）希望巴塞盡快解決：「長此下去對教練、球員、球迷都不好。」<br />\n<br />\n「華維迪的境況在過去數天愈來愈差。我跟巴塞主席巴度姆沒有太多交流，但關係不錯，跟巴塞中人也一樣。」小白續說。<br />\n<br />\n對於昔日戰友沙維執起教鞭短短日子便有機會入主巴塞，35歲的恩尼斯達坦言：「只有他自己知道準備好了沒。朗奴高文、沙維都曾效力巴塞，一個經驗較為豐富，但這不是決定性的條件。」"},{"pid":"a9494360b32ebdc6079e326c2c3a9eb91de7cfc7","tid":1822571,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"feo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a812857df914ea9cb5f55084064c1e6948b7fb6","tid":1822571,"uid":31626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:02:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f984547e3b3d01dd8e477cfa9c3ed946ecf7db4","tid":1822571,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:06:20.000Z","msg":"華維迪唔是condom <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5767eb27b0ab0261841d0a46788f59f25c85b9e7","tid":1822571,"uid":134997,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a9494360b32ebdc6079e326c2c3a9eb91de7cfc7","tid":1822571,"uid":36461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T04:57:03.000Z","msg":"feo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-13T05:10:11.000Z","msg":"vvd por favor qu&eacute;date<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid"